						<div class="postbody">ASL forgets the old value of carry and moves bit 7 into carry. If you open the debugger in FCEUX for Windows and &quot;Step Into&quot; through shifting $14 to the left five times, you'll see this:<br /><br />Initial: A=14 C=don't care<br />ASL 1: A=28 C=0<br />ASL 2: A=50 C=0<br />ASL 3: A=A0 C=0<br />ASL 4: A=40 C=1<br />ASL 5: A=80 C=0</div>

